  "description": "<p>如今在一个遍布Wifi的城市里，智能手机遍可以满足人类各式各样的要求。可是如果这些Wifi信号可以被人类的肉眼所看见又会是怎样一番景象呢？ 艺术家Nickolay Lamm 用摄影艺术为我们呈现了这一壮观的视图。Lamm在天体生物学家和前NASA工作人员M. Browning Vogel的帮助下想象出了由智能手机和路由器产生的Wifi波。这些波成环状分布，从发射点散发出不同的颜色，在世界各地形成了五彩的雾气。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ef4e1d0/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245460.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C+Wifi+%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E8%A7%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245460.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C+Wifi+%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E8%A7%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245460.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C+Wifi+%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E8%A7%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245460.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C+Wifi+%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E8%A7%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245460.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C+Wifi+%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%E5%BE%97%E8%A7%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/s